title: Written In The Stars Anthology
description: Immerse yourself in new worlds and discover hidden places, from far-off realms to different neighborhoods. Cast spells, break curses ... or even play the drum! And forge friendships with fae, angels, muses, or simply the boy next door.Join the award-winning and USA Today bestselling authors of Written in the Stars—a young adult contemporary, paranormal, and fantasy romance anthology—on these adventures and more. Packed with 16 stories, the collection is composed exclusively of full-length, first-in-series tales, introducing you to worlds beyond its pages. Some might call this collection your reading destiny, but we say it's Written in the Stars ...Titles listed
author: Emily Camp
